value: Central America, South America: Nicaragua to sw Ecuador

Resident [[i]melanorrhoa [/i]group] on the Caribbean slope of extreme eastern Honduras (Gracias a Dios), Nicaragua, and Costa Rica; and [[i]urochrysia [/i]group] from Panama (locally on both slopes) and western Colombia south to northwestern Ecuador.
Tropical Lowland Evergreen Forest (0-900 m; Tropical Zone).
